                <p>Zelio, a growing name in the electric vehicle market, has launched its new electric scooter, the Eeva ZX+, in India. With rising demand for electric mobility solutions, the Eeva ZX+ aims to provide urban commuters with an eco-friendly, convenient, and affordable transportation option. The scooter boasts a sleek design, impressive range, and user-friendly features, making it a strong contender in the country’s electric two-wheeler market.</p>
